843 plan may excuse the failure to hire any individual and no such system
844 or plan may require or permit the termination of employment on the
845 basis of age. No such plan which covers less than twenty employees may
846 reduce the group hospital, surgical or medical insurance coverage
847 provided under the plan to any employee who has reached the age of
